Use Datastar patterns (`data-on:click`, `@post`, signals) consistent with the rest of the app. Look at the existing fragments for examples.

**Important Datastar patterns to follow:**
- Buttons use `data-on:click="@post('/api/...')"` for actions
- File uploads may need a different approach ΓÇö check how the setup page handles `programJson` signal
- SSE responses use `patchElements` with selectors

## Step 6: Wire it all together

In `src/index.ts`:
- The `handleProgramSSE` function needs to pass any necessary state to the import section
- After import, re-render the Program page with the new program data

## Conventions
- Domain functions are pure: data in, data out
- D1 queries use prepared statements
- Import `escapeHtml`, `escapeAttr`, `truncate` from `../utils/html`
- Dark theme: #141210 background, #e8e4df text
- Fragments return HTML strings with Datastar attributes
